high_descs: Take a right at the wall and walk to the vanity with the sink.
Pick up the green candle to the left of the sink on the counter.
Turn around, take a left at the door and turn left at the toilet to face the drawers under the vanity counter.
Open the bottom drawer under the sink, put the green candle inside and close the drawer.
Turn right and walk to the toilet on the left.
Pick up the green candle from the left side of the toilet tank.
Turn around, take a right at the wall and turn right to face the drawers under the vanity.
Open the bottom drawer under the sink, put the green candle to the right of the other candle and close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put two candles in a drawer.

high_descs: Take a step forward and turn right to find a candle on the sink counter.
Pick up the candle from the counter.
Turn around, walk towards the door, turn left and walk to the toilet on your left.
Pull out the bottom drawer below the sink, place the candle in it, and close it.
Take a step to the right to face the toilet.
Pick up the candle on the toilet tank.
Take several steps to the right to find the bottom drawer below the sink.
Open the drawer, place the candle next to the other candle, and close it.
anns.task_desc: Place the two candles into the bottom drawer below the sink.

high_descs: Turn to the right and face the counter to the left of the sink.
Pick the candle up from the counter.
Go to the right and stand in front of the counter to the right of the sink.
Open the drawer, second from the right, under the sink and put the candle in and shut the drawer.
Move to the right and face the toilet.
Pick the candle up from the back of the toilet.
Move to the left and face the drawer under the right side of the sink.
Open the drawer below the right side of the sink and put the candle in and shut the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put two candles in a drawer.
